  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1022">
<l>āḷviṉaiyu māṉṟa vaṟivu meṉaviraṇṭi</l>
<l>ṉīḷviṉaiyā ṉīḷuṅ kuṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One's family is raised by untiring perseverance in both effort and wise contrivances.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
